Package: rPuma
Type: Package
Title: R interface for PUMA software
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Krunoslav Juraic
Maintainer: The package maintainer <kjuraic@irb.hr>
Description: R interface for comand-line PUMA code.
      Calculation of optical constants (absorption and index of refraction) and
      thicknes of thin by pointwise unconstrained optimization from.
      Transmission/Reflection measurements.
      Transmission/Reflection data formation for PUMA input.
      Optimization parameters list construction.
      PUMA run.
      Importing PUMA results in R.
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports:
  stats,
  utils
